<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title_display }} — 図解（v1）</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            brand: { dark: '#0c4a6e', mid: '#0369a1', light: '#e0f2fe' }
          },
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ['"Hiragino Sans"', '"Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN"', 'Meiryo', 'sans-serif']
          }
        }
      }
    };
  </script>
  <style>
    @media print {
      .no-print { display: none !important; }
      body { background: #fff !important; }
      .shadow-lg, .shadow-md, .shadow-sm { box-shadow: none !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 antialiased">
  <header class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-dark via-brand-mid to-sky-600 text-white shadow-lg">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-10 pb-10 pt-10 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-sky-200/90">ミクス発売記事ベース・PMDA添付文書抜粋（自動生成）</p>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight break-words sm:text-3xl">{{ title_display }}</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-base text-sky-100">効能（4）・薬効薬理（18）・臨床成績（17）・副作用（11）・用法・相互作用（6・7・10）</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6">
    <p class="mb-8 rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-amber-950">
      {{ disclaimer }}
    </p>

    <div class="mb-10 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 px-4 py-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-600 shadow-sm">
      <p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-500">生成</span> {{ generated_at }} / <span class="font-semibold text-slate-500">stable_id</span> <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-[11px]">{{ stable_id }}</code></p>
      <p class="mt-1"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-500">ミクス</span> <a class="font-medium text-sky-800 underline decoration-sky-600 underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-950" href="{{ rss_link }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ rss_link }}</a></p>
      {% if pmda_url %}
      <p class="mt-1"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-500">PMDA</span> <a class="font-medium text-sky-800 underline decoration-sky-600 underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-950" href="{{ pmda_url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ pmda_url }}</a></p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if source_pdf_url %}
      <p class="mt-1"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-500">添付文書 PDF</span> <a class="font-medium text-sky-800 underline decoration-sky-600 underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-950" href="{{ source_pdf_url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ source_pdf_url }}</a></p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">1</span>
        識別・製品情報（添付文書 章4より前）
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_ident or "（識別領域の自動抽出なし）" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">4</span>
        効能又は効果
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_4 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">18</span>
        薬効薬理
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_18 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">17</span>
        臨床成績
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_17 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">11</span>
        副作用
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_11 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-mid text-sm text-white">6–10</span>
        用法・用量・相互作用（メモ）
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ section_6710 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 pt-8 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
      出典: PMDA 公開の添付文書（抜粋・自動生成）。診療・服薬は医師・薬剤師の指示および最新の添付文書に従ってください。KEGG 等の二次出典は v1 では用いていません。
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
